manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "rust-server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "rust-server"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.56"
rand = "0.8.5"
reqwest = "0.11.11"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "3.2.8"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.rocket]
version = "=0.5.0-rc.2"
features = ["json"]
optional = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.5.13"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "macros", "offline", "any", "postgres", "mysql", "sqlite", "mssql"]
optional = false
default-features = false
